import React from 'react';

interface MollyAvatarProps {
  size?: number;
  animate?: boolean;
}

const MollyAvatar: React.FC<MollyAvatarProps> = ({ size = 60, animate = true }) => {
  return (
    <svg
      width={size}
      height={size}
      viewBox="0 0 100 100"
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      style={animate ? { animation: 'mollyBob 2.6s ease-in-out infinite' } : {}}
    >
      <defs>
        {/* Main body gradient - deep green to bright green like the character */}
        <radialGradient id="bodyGrad" cx="40%" cy="30%" r="65%">
          <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#7ecb3a" />
          <stop offset="50%" stopColor="#4ea32a" />
          <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#2e6e14" />
        </radialGradient>
        {/* Shine highlight */}
        <radialGradient id="shineGrad" cx="40%" cy="30%" r="55%">
          <stop offset="0%" stopColor="rgba(255,255,255,0.35)" />
          <stop offset="100%" stopColor="rgba(255,255,255,0)" />
        </radialGradient>
        {/* Eye gradient - dark brown */}
        <radialGradient id="eyeGrad" cx="35%" cy="30%" r="60%">
          <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#5c3317" />
          <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#1a0a00" />
        </radialGradient>
        {/* Leaf on top gradient */}
        <radialGradient id="leafGrad" cx="50%" cy="30%" r="60%">
          <stop offset="0%" stopColor="#9de040" />
          <stop offset="100%" stopColor="#4ea32a" />
        </radialGradient>
        <filter id="softShadow" x="-20%" y="-20%" width="140%" height="140%">
          <feDropShadow dx="0" dy="3" stdDeviation="3" floodColor="rgba(0,0,0,0.25)" />
        </filter>
      </defs>

      {/* ── Body: rounded teardrop / leaf shape like Molly ── */}
      <ellipse
        cx="50" cy="57"
        rx="34" ry="36"
        fill="url(#bodyGrad)"
        filter="url(#softShadow)"
      />
      {/* Top pointed part of teardrop */}
      <path
        d="M50,22 C44,30 30,38 32,50 C34,62 66,62 68,50 C70,38 56,30 50,22 Z"
        fill="url(#bodyGrad)"
      />
      {/* Shine overlay */}
      <ellipse cx="50" cy="50" rx="34" ry="38" fill="url(#shineGrad)" />

      {/* Leaf vein line down center */}
      <line
        x1="50" y1="25"
        x2="50" y2="80"
        stroke="rgba(30,80,10,0.25)"
        strokeWidth="1.5"
        strokeLinecap="round"
      />

      {/* ── Sprout on top ── */}
      {/* Stem */}
      <path
        d="M50,22 Q50,14 50,10"
        stroke="#4ea32a"
        strokeWidth="2"
        fill="none"
        strokeLinecap="round"
      />
      {/* Left leaf of sprout */}
      <path
        d="M50,14 Q44,8 40,10 Q42,16 50,14 Z"
        fill="url(#leafGrad)"
      />
      {/* Right leaf of sprout */}
      <path
        d="M50,12 Q56,6 60,8 Q58,14 50,12 Z"
        fill="url(#leafGrad)"
      />

      {/* ── Arms ── */}
      {/* Left arm */}
      <ellipse
        cx="18" cy="60"
        rx="8" ry="6"
        fill="url(#bodyGrad)"
        transform="rotate(-20, 18, 60)"
      />
      {/* Right arm */}
      <ellipse
        cx="82" cy="60"
        rx="8" ry="6"
        fill="url(#bodyGrad)"
        transform="rotate(20, 82, 60)"
      />

      {/* ── Legs / feet ── */}
      {/* Left foot */}
      <ellipse cx="41" cy="90" rx="8" ry="6" fill="url(#bodyGrad)" />
      {/* Right foot */}
      <ellipse cx="59" cy="90" rx="8" ry="6" fill="url(#bodyGrad)" />

      {/* ── Eyebrows (subtle arched) ── */}
      <path
        d="M36,44 Q40,41 44,43"
        stroke="rgba(30,80,10,0.5)"
        strokeWidth="1.5"
        fill="none"
        strokeLinecap="round"
      />
      <path
        d="M56,43 Q60,41 64,44"
        stroke="rgba(30,80,10,0.5)"
        strokeWidth="1.5"
        fill="none"
        strokeLinecap="round"
      />

      {/* ── Eyes ── */}
      {/* Left eye white */}
      <ellipse cx="40" cy="52" rx="7" ry="8" fill="white" />
      {/* Right eye white */}
      <ellipse cx="60" cy="52" rx="7" ry="8" fill="white" />
      {/* Left pupil */}
      <ellipse cx="41" cy="53" rx="4.5" ry="5.5" fill="url(#eyeGrad)" />
      {/* Right pupil */}
      <ellipse cx="61" cy="53" rx="4.5" ry="5.5" fill="url(#eyeGrad)" />
      {/* Left eye shine */}
      <circle cx="42.5" cy="50.5" r="1.8" fill="white" />
      {/* Right eye shine */}
      <circle cx="62.5" cy="50.5" r="1.8" fill="white" />

      {/* ── Smile ── */}
      <path
        d="M43,65 Q50,71 57,65"
        stroke="rgba(30,80,10,0.6)"
        strokeWidth="2"
        fill="none"
        strokeLinecap="round"
      />
    </svg>
  );
};

export default MollyAvatar;
